homepage.tagline.message: Cloud Native Architecture Engineering Playbook & Benchmark Reports

homepage.description.message: Cloud Native Architecture Engineering Playbook & Benchmark Reports — EKS infrastructure optimization, Agentic AI, AIOps, performance benchmarks

homepage.domains.subtitle.message: Explore comprehensive guides across seven core technical domains with quantitative benchmark reports.

homepage.quickstart.description.message: New to cloud native engineering? Start with the introduction for a full overview, then explore benchmark reports for data-driven decisions.

homepage.features.infrastructure.descrip.message: Gateway API adoption, CoreDNS optimization, Cilium CNI networking, Karpenter autoscaling, East-West traffic optimization, and cost management.

homepage.features.observability.descript.message: GitOps cluster operations, node monitoring, EKS debugging, high availability architecture, Pod health lifecycle, and scheduling strategies.

homepage.features.agentic.description.message: Production GenAI platform with vLLM/MoE serving, llm-d distributed inference, Inference Gateway, Milvus RAG, Kagent AI agents, and MLOps pipelines.

homepage.features.hybrid.description.message: Hybrid nodes adoption, SR-IOV DGX H200 high-performance networking, shared file storage, and Harbor container registry integration.

homepage.features.security.description.message: Identity-First Security, GuardDuty threat detection, Kyverno policy management, supply chain security for enterprise Kubernetes.

homepage.features.aiops.description.message: AIOps strategies for EKS, intelligent observability stack with ADOT/AMP/AMG, AIDLC framework with Kiro and MCP, predictive scaling and auto-recovery.

homepage.features.rosa.description.message: Red Hat OpenShift Service on AWS installation guide, security configuration, and compliance management.

homepage.features.benchmarks.description.message: Quantitative performance benchmarks: CNI comparison (Cilium vs VPC CNI), Gateway API implementations, AI/ML workloads, and infrastructure performance.
